<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,151,680]" pageId="8" pageNumber="269">
Some characters (e.g. medial, pronotal depression) can be found also in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Bílý, 2019" authorityName="Bílý" authorityYear="2019" box="[1174,1275,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="269" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" sensu="stricto" status="s. str." subGenus="Anthaxia">
